      <p><em>Within Reach</em> makes the hard work of recovery easy, accessible and private.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Users will reflect on episodes of binging and purging with our guided entries. Each entry walks a user through the core steps of dialectical behavior therapy including mindfulness, emotional regulation, and distress tolerance.</li><br>
          <li>Users can quickly and easily access the online and mobile app which makes it easy to practice DBT skills traditionally found in <a href="https://www.newharbinger.com/dialectical-behavior-therapy-skills-workbook-bulimia">The Dialectical Behavior Therapy Skills Workbook</a>.</li>
